message.content:
The list of verbs (in their base forms) associated with a computer program could include:

1. Code
2. Compile
3. Decrypt
4. Debug
5. Decode
6. Encrypt
7. Execute
8. Implement
9. Initialize 
10 Install 
11 Modify 
12 Optimize  
13 Perform  
14 Reboot     
15 Recover   
16 Run          
17 Save         
18 Search      
19 Secure     
20 Systematize    
21 Test        
22 Uninstall        
23 Update       
24 Upgrade        

Note that not all the above verbs may be applicable for every type of computer program or scenario, however, they provide a comprehensive and general understanding of actions related to programming endeavors and software usage.
